        },
        "item_8ADzLw": {
          "type": "item",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Are facial masks suitable for all skin types?",
            "content": "<p>Yes, our masks are formulated for all skin types, including sensitive skin. The active ingredients (Hyaluronic Acid, AHA, Aloe Vera) are selected for their effectiveness and high tolerance.</p>"
